nodes.text: Old-fashioned protato salad was a lunch side at Dex's Diner on the planet Coruscant prior to the eatery's destruction during the first two years of the Galactic Empire's reign. Made with protatoes, the salad was sold for 2.7 credits and was made in a style that was considered old-fashioned.
Old-fashioned protato salad was introduced in "Dining at Dex's," a 2009 Hyperspace-exclusive article which was written by Gregory Walker and formatted as an in-universe menu.
